attributes.mlflow.spanInputs:
{"database_schema": ""Description for table: Token"
type Token @entity {
  "Unique identifier for the token."
  id: ID!
  "Version number of the token."
  version: BigInt!
  "Type of sales associated with the token."
  salesType: BigInt!
  "Unique identifier for the token within its edition."
  tokenId: BigInt!
  "Number of times the token has been transferred."
  transferCount: BigInt!
  "Specific number of the token within its edition."
  editionNumber: String!
  "Edition details of the token."
  edition: Edition!
  "URI pointing to the token's metadata."
  tokenURI: String!
  "Metadata associated with the token."
  metadata: MetaData
  "Timestamp when the token was created."
  birthTimestamp: BigInt!
  "Initial sale value of the token in Ethereum."
  primaryValueInEth: BigDecimal!
  "Total value of all purchases of the token."
  totalPurchaseValue: BigDecimal!
  "Total number of purchases of the token."
  totalPurchaseCount: BigInt!
  "Highest value of a secondary sale in Ethereum."
  largestSecondaryValueInEth: BigDecimal!
  "Highest sale price of the token in Ethereum."
  largestSalePriceEth: BigDecimal!
  "Price of the last sale in Ethereum."
  lastSalePriceInEth: BigDecimal!
  "Timestamp of the last transfer of the token."
  lastTransferTimestamp: BigInt!
  "Current owner of the token."
  currentOwner: Collector
  "List of all previous owners of the token."
  allOwners: [Collector!]!
  "Events related to the transfer of the token."
  transfers: [TransferEvent!]!
  "Events associated with the token."
  tokenEvents: [TokenEvent!]!
  "Current open offer for the token."
  openOffer: TokenOffer
  "Current highest bidder for the token."
  currentTopBidder: Bytes
  "Account of the artist who created the token."
  artistAccount: Bytes!
  "Indicates if the edition is currently active."
  editionActive: Boolean!
  "Indicates if approval for the token has been revoked."
  revokedApproval: Boolean!
  "Indicates if the token is currently listed for sale."
  isListed: Boolean!
  "Price at which the token is listed."
  listPrice: BigDecimal
  "Collector who listed the token."
  lister: Collector
  "Timestamp when the token was listed."
  listingTimestamp: BigInt
  "Details of the token's listing."
  listing: ListedToken
  "Contract of the creator of the token."
  creatorContract: CreatorContract
}"}
